<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span><span class="c2">(فرصافه عظمٌ وقذته ... قطع اللجين وفوقه ذهب)</span><a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>